## Public Member Functions

### getTagID() {#a6386ca6c50ec4ef5d9a0f13e7fe8f0c9}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>uint32&#95;t llvm::OperandBundleUse::getTagID () const</>}
  labels = {["inline"]}>
Return the tag of this operand bundle as an integer.

Operand bundle tags are interned by <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/llvmcontextimpl/#a6ca6e14339dfb653b003a458b80a4802">LLVMContextImpl::getOrInsertBundleTag</a>, and this function returns the unique integer getOrInsertBundleTag associated the tag of this operand bundle to.
